{"tid":1590750,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"以武制暴既手足入一入黎","createTime":"2019-09-24T01:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T03:09:11.000Z","uid":6111,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9a4207035c0e723f03c9cc958d6f9d46bf40fb2c","tid":1590750,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:14:18.000Z","msg":"各位手足 我本人十分認同及支持以武制暴<br />\n但希望大家以武制暴之前諗下用咩武力去制暴<br />\n如果對面係得把口係度屌既就由鳩佢<br />\n如果對面出手但冇武器打拳頭交既我地都打返拳頭交就算<br />\n如果對面開始拎武器 理佢拎藤條又好棍又好 一律當佢地刀手看待 唔搞出人命就得<br />\n記住 我地係抗爭者 係雞蛋<br />\n我地唔係紅衛兵 更加唔係黑警<br />\n如果你地話我係民意撚就大錯特錯<br />\n係依家依一刻民意根本就好難再完變<br />\n我提出以上既要求只係棍各位手足時刻保持理性 要記住我地係為乜野而企出黎 係為左乜野已迫不得已地使用合適武力黎<span style=\"font-size: large;\">制止暴力</span>"},{"pid":"907d4123430c16bb702701428c8b2cb61e7e1959","tid":1590750,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:19:42.000Z","msg":"1/1001"},{"pid":"86b9f3dd7e140cab04aa6d0785de2882c22795c5","tid":1590750,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:22:26.000Z","msg":"2/1001"},{"pid":"17abc3999a357e8bdb81215a03558fe27d239af3","tid":1590750,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:36:43.000Z","msg":"3/1001"},{"pid":"61cd6d363ba34ca14155d1e8515a4eea2daed3ea","tid":1590750,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:39:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">做得忍者，一定要識保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sjzvXH8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsjzvXH8.jpg&h=b6574070&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ede097961ddf96e51aec5463d62e159eb86e2a4a","tid":1590750,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:09:11.000Z","msg":"4/1001"}]}